cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes a model for inferring new facts from existing knowledge graphs through explainable reasoning processes. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and database systems (cs.DB) to handle the knowledge graphs. Additionally, information retrieval (cs.IR) is relevant as the model retrieves relevant evidence during the reasoning process.
